ygData.messageBody:
The Korean server sucks. Always kana the server down crap. I know its the
limit of people, but rather than spending time clicking the join/create
button I rather spend time playing in open server. if the open another
server in Singapore or elsewhere, or improve the limit cap then I'll go
back to realm.
